data.description: 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath WATERFRONT RANCH located in the Ballylinn Farms neighborhood on the Elizabeth River. This gorgeous property had the kitchen remodeled in 2021 with high end fixtures, granite countertops, marble backsplash and more! The family room is LARGE with a gas fireplace and is just off the stunning sunroom offering great water views so you can enjoy at an time of the year. The primary bathroom was also updated in 2021. Out back the backyard is perfect for entertaining featuring a large deck, gazebo with electricity, 2 separate docks, boathouse all on deep water. To top it all of the garage opens from the front and back allowing a great space for storage, toys or vehicles. Located near Norfolk State University, Virginia Zoo, shopping, entertainment and more!
